snippet.title: Swift: Firebase 3 - How to Group Messages Per User (Ep 10)
snippet.description:
Lets start off the week by further completing the main messages view to include the user's name, profile image, and timestamp.  Finally I'll show you how to group the messages together so that only the latest message will show for the user. Have fun.

Previous Episode 9:
https://youtu.be/cw0gLZHJOiE

All episodes for Firebase 3 series:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0dzCUj1L5JEfHqwjBV0XFb9qx9cGXwkq
